Package com.apgar.common.lib.constraint

package com.apgar.common.lib.constraint
Defines constants for EBX, including common variable names, environment variable identifiers, and workflow process constants.
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    BundledConstraint
    Class that allows the use of the messages of file Bundle.
    GreaterOrEqualThanConstraint
    Greater or Equal Than Constraint used to compare two fields.
    GreaterThanConstraint
    Greater Than Constraint used to compare two fields.
    MandatoryIfOtherFieldEmpty
    Constraint that checks if one field is filled, the other field should be empty.
    MandatoryOnOtherFieldValueConstraint
    Constraint that sets mandatory the field it is defined on if the parameter mandatoringField field has the same value as the parameter mandatoringValue.
    MandatoryOnOtherFieldValueOtherwiseEmptyConstraint
    Constraint that sets mandatory the field it is defined on if the parameter mandatoringField has the same value as the mandatoringValue parameter, otherwise it should be empty.
    NotMandatoryOnOtherFieldValueConstraint
    Constraint that sets mandatory the field it is defined on if the parameter mandatoringField field has a different value than the mandatoringValue parameter.
    UniquenessCheckWithConditionConstraintOnTable
    Constraint that checks for record uniqueness across the table it is defined on and based on the fields passed as input parameters in the data model.
